---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Experience - Julia Kang" description="Explore Julia Kang's professional experience including research positions, development work, and leadership roles.">
	<section class="experience-hero">
		<div class="container">
			<h1 class="page-title">Professional Experience</h1>
			<p class="page-subtitle">
				Building impactful solutions through research, development, and leadership across biomedical research, AI applications, and software engineering.
			</p>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="timeline">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="timeline-container">
				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker current"></div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<div class="timeline-header">
							<h3 class="company">Mead Johnson x The Data Mine</h3>
							<span class="duration">Aug 2025 – Present</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="position">Undergraduate Researcher / Developer</h4>
						<ul class="achievements">
							<li>Collaborated with Mead Johnson in a multidisciplinary team to design and implement a <strong>Python-based peptide database</strong> for biomedical research applications</li>
							<li>Developed <strong>data pipelines</strong> to integrate peptide data from multiple open-source repositories, consolidating structural, biochemical, and trait-specific characteristics into a centralized resource</li>
							<li>Enhanced data accessibility for biomedical researchers through systematic database architecture and efficient data processing workflows</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="tech-stack">
							<span class="tech">Python</span>
							<span class="tech">Data Pipelines</span>
							<span class="tech">Database Design</span>
							<span class="tech">Biomedical Research</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker current"></div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<div class="timeline-header">
							<h3 class="company">Purdue University Vertically Integrated Projects</h3>
							<span class="duration">Aug 2025 – Present</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="position">Undergraduate Researcher / Developer</h4>
						<ul class="achievements">
							<li>Conducted research with faculty and peers on applying <strong>AI techniques to disaster response</strong>, focusing on disaster image classification models using <strong>PyTorch</strong></li>
							<li>Synthesized academic literature on AI for disaster detection, damage assessment, and emergency response in weekly research meetings to present findings and refine methodologies</li>
							<li>Contributed to the development of machine learning models that can assist in rapid disaster assessment and emergency response coordination</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="tech-stack">
							<span class="tech">PyTorch</span>
							<span class="tech">Computer Vision</span>
							<span class="tech">Disaster Response AI</span>
							<span class="tech">Research & Development</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<div class="timeline-header">
							<h3 class="company">BucketList</h3>
							<span class="duration">Sep 2024 – Jun 2025</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="position">Developer</h4>
						<ul class="achievements">
							<li><strong>$1,000 commissioned</strong> goal-focused community platform app for client business inquiry with Purdue ACM SIGAPP</li>
							<li>Created the <strong>Community Board page</strong> using React Native and connected it to AWS backend using Prisma and NodeJS for the backend</li>
							<li>Delivered a scalable mobile application that enables users to create, share, and track personal and community goals</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="tech-stack">
							<span class="tech">React Native</span>
							<span class="tech">AWS</span>
							<span class="tech">Prisma</span>
							<span class="tech">Node.js</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="timeline-item">
					<div class="timeline-marker"></div>
					<div class="timeline-content">
						<div class="timeline-header">
							<h3 class="company">Gunn Computer Science Capstone</h3>
							<span class="duration">Dec 2022 – May 2024</span>
						</div>
						<h4 class="position">Student Lead</h4>
						<ul class="achievements">
							<li>Deployed <strong>alumni networking NextJS-TypeScript web app</strong> with Supabase SQL database hosted on Netlify (<a href="https://alumni.gunnhigh.school" target="_blank" class="link">alumni.gunnhigh.school</a>)</li>
							<li><strong>Delegated tasks and coordinated meetings</strong> for development and discussed features with 40+ community members</li>
							<li>Led a student team in creating a platform that connects current students with alumni for mentorship and career guidance</li>
						</ul>
						<div class="tech-stack">
							<span class="tech">Next.js</span>
							<span class="tech">TypeScript</span>
							<span class="tech">Supabase</span>
							<span class="tech">Leadership</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="leadership">
		<div class="container">
			<h2 class="section-title">Leadership & Extracurriculars</h2>
			<div class="leadership-grid">
				<div class="leadership-card">
					<div class="leadership-header">
						<h3 class="organization">Purdue Society of Asian Scientists and Engineers (SASE)</h3>
						<span class="role-duration">Sep 2024 – Present</span>
					</div>
					<h4 class="role">Secretary, Admin</h4>
					<ul class="leadership-achievements">
						<li>Partnered with president and department leads on <strong>long-term strategic vision</strong> of the 350+ member organization</li>
						<li>Managed weekly communications, documented key decisions at board meetings, oversaw event preparation</li>
						<li>Facilitated coordination between different departments and committees to ensure smooth operations</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="impact-stats">
						<div class="stat">
							<span class="stat-number">350+</span>
							<span class="stat-label">Members</span>
						</div>
						<div class="stat">
							<span class="stat-number">Weekly</span>
							<span class="stat-label">Communications</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="leadership-card">
					<div class="leadership-header">
						<h3 class="organization">United Computations</h3>
						<span class="role-duration">May 2023 – May 2024</span>
					</div>
					<h4 class="role">President, Lead Organizer</h4>
					<ul class="leadership-achievements">
						<li>Coordinated weekly club meetings and activities promoting various computing topics</li>
						<li>Organized a <strong>24-hour in-person student hackathon with 150+ attendees</strong>, partnering with Major League Hacking</li>
						<li>Raised $250 through a bake sale, managed logistics and teacher shifts, and hosted an AI/ML workshop for attendees</li>
					</ul>
					<div class="impact-stats">
						<div class="stat">
							<span class="stat-number">150+</span>
							<span class="stat-label">Hackathon Attendees</span>
						</div>
						<div class="stat">
							<span class="stat-number">24hr</span>
							<span class="stat-label">Event Duration</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="skills-used">
		<div class="container">
			<h2 class="section-title">Key Skills Demonstrated</h2>
			<div class="skills-showcase">
				<div class="skill-group">
					<h3>Technical Skills</h3>
					<div class="skill-list">
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Python Development & Data Processing</span>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Machine Learning with PyTorch</span>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Mobile App Development (React Native)</span>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Full-Stack Web Development</span>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Cloud Infrastructure (AWS)</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<div class="skill-group">
					<h3>Leadership & Soft Skills</h3>
					<div class="skill-list">
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Team Leadership & Project Management</span>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Strategic Planning & Vision</span>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Stakeholder Communication</span>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Research & Analysis</span>
						</div>
						<div class="skill-item">
							<span>Cross-functional Collaboration</span>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.experience-hero {
		padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
		background: #fafaf8;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
	}

	.container {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 2rem;
	}

	.page-title {
		font-size: 2rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #2a2a2a;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.page-subtitle {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		color: #6a6a6a;
		max-width: 700px;
		line-height: 1.7;
	}

	.timeline {
		padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
		background: #fafaf8;
	}

	.timeline-container {
		position: relative;
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.timeline-container::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 10px;
		top: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		width: 2px;
		background: #d4d4d4;
	}

	.timeline-item {
		position: relative;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		padding-left: 40px;
	}

	.timeline-marker {
		position: absolute;
		left: 5px;
		top: 8px;
		width: 12px;
		height: 12px;
		background: #e4e4e4;
		border: 2px solid #fafaf8;
		border-radius: 50%;
	}

	.timeline-marker.current {
		background: #2a2a2a;
	}

	.timeline-content {
		background: transparent;
		border: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 1.5rem;
	}

	.timeline-header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: flex-start;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		padding-bottom: 1rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
	}

	.company {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #2a2a2a;
		margin: 0;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.duration {
		background: transparent;
		color: #6a6a6a;
		padding: 0;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	.position {
		color: #4a4a4a;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.achievements {
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		padding-left: 0;
	}

	.achievements li {
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #4a4a4a;
		list-style: none;
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 1.2rem;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.achievements li::before {
		content: '—';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: #2a2a2a;
		font-weight: normal;
	}

	.tech-stack {
		display: flex;
		flex-wrap: wrap;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.tech {
		background: transparent;
		color: #6a6a6a;
		padding: 0.3rem 0.7rem;
		border: 1px solid #d4d4d4;
		border-radius: 4px;
		font-size: 0.8rem;
		font-weight: 400;
	}

	.link {
		color: #2a2a2a;
		text-decoration: underline;
		font-weight: 400;
	}

	.link:hover {
		color: #6a6a6a;
	}

	.leadership {
		padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
		background: #fafaf8;
		border-top: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
	}

	.section-title {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
		color: #2a2a2a;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: -0.02em;
	}

	.leadership-grid {
		display: grid;
		gap: 2.5rem;
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.leadership-card {
		background: transparent;
		border: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 2rem;
	}

	.leadership-header {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: space-between;
		align-items: flex-start;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		padding-bottom: 1rem;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
	}

	.organization {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #2a2a2a;
		margin: 0;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.role-duration {
		background: transparent;
		color: #6a6a6a;
		padding: 0;
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		font-weight: 400;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}

	.role {
		color: #4a4a4a;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		margin-bottom: 1rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
		font-weight: 500;
	}

	.leadership-achievements {
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		padding-left: 0;
	}

	.leadership-achievements li {
		margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
		line-height: 1.7;
		color: #4a4a4a;
		list-style: none;
		position: relative;
		padding-left: 1.2rem;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
	}

	.leadership-achievements li::before {
		content: '—';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: #2a2a2a;
		font-weight: normal;
	}

	.impact-stats {
		display: flex;
		gap: 2rem;
		border-top: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
		padding-top: 1.5rem;
	}

	.stat {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.25rem;
	}

	.stat-number {
		font-size: 1.25rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		color: #2a2a2a;
	}

	.stat-label {
		font-size: 0.85rem;
		color: #6a6a6a;
		text-transform: none;
		letter-spacing: normal;
	}

	.skills-used {
		padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
		background: #fafaf8;
		border-top: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
	}

	.skills-showcase {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
		gap: 2rem;
		max-width: 700px;
		margin: 0 auto;
	}

	.skill-group {
		background: transparent;
		border: 1px solid #e4e4e4;
		border-radius: 8px;
		padding: 2rem;
	}

	.skill-group h3 {
		font-size: 1rem;
		color: #2a2a2a;
		margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		letter-spacing: -0.01em;
	}

	.skill-list {
		display: grid;
		gap: 0.75rem;
	}

	.skill-item {
		padding: 0;
		background: transparent;
		border: none;
		font-size: 0.9rem;
		color: #4a4a4a;
	}

	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.page-title {
			font-size: 1.75rem;
		}

		.timeline-container::before {
			left: 8px;
		}

		.timeline-marker {
			left: 3px;
		}

		.timeline-item {
			padding-left: 35px;
		}

		.timeline-header {
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 0.5rem;
		}

		.leadership-header {
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 0.5rem;
		}

		.timeline-content, .leadership-card, .skill-group {
			padding: 1.25rem;
		}

		.skills-showcase {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}

		.container {
			padding: 0 1rem;
		}
	}
</style>